node.title: One dead after cyclist and vehicle crash in south Taranaki
node.description: A person has died in a crash between a vehicle and a cyclist in south Taranaki on Tuesday morning.
node.content:
["A person has died in a crash between a vehicle and a cyclist in south Taranaki on Tuesday morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Emergency services were called to South Road in Warea about 10.40am.", "Police said the road would be closed for some time.", "Diversions are in place at Mid Puniho Road and at Parihaka.", "The police serious crash unit has been advised."]
